used to define basic notions of causality and to provide a definition of a\ndynamical black hole in these theories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jan 2021 19:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Mar 2021 08:42:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-21"}
