lex wells, and\nhydraulic fracturing simulations. Extension to other systems can be handled\nquite naturally. We demonstrate the efficiency and scalability of the resulting\nsolvers through numerical examples of difficult, field-scale problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Jan 2021 19:11:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2021 02:56:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 31 Jul 2021 03:11:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-04"}
