oral networks, and\nnetwork of networks. The intention of this paper is to offer an overview of\nthese applications, as well as the basic theory of percolation transition on\nnetwork systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 00:59:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-20"}
