 charm\nquarks with strange quarks in the QGP plays an important role in $D_{s}^{\\pm}$\nmeson production in heavy-ion collisions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 03:06:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 May 2021 04:08:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 18 Jun 2021 01:44:42 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 22 Jul 2021 04:15:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-01"}
