 theoretical model for noisy Hopf bifurcation\nwherein the control parameter is continuously varied at different rates to\nstudy the effect of rate of change of parameter on EWS. Similar results,\nincluding the hyperexponential scaling, are observed in the model as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 04:33:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-29"}
