 to\nalleviate over-smoothing, and further verify the feasibility for designing GNNs\nwith our unified optimization framework.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 08:06:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-29"}
