alue of $\\Omega_k$\nshifts a little bit from $-0.049$ to $-0.036$, and the parameters in our model\nare not degenerate with $\\Omega_k$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 09:10:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 3 Apr 2021 00:28:54 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 16 Apr 2021 06:35:21 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 21 May 2021 01:05:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-26"}
