 strong intradimer and weak monomer-dimer couplings. We found the\nrefined values for the coupling constants of Cu$_3$(P$_2$O$_6$OH)$_2$ by\nmatching the theoretical results with the available experimental data for the\nmagnetization and magnetic susceptibility in a wide range of temperatures and\nmagnetic fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jan 2021 10:59:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Apr 2021 08:40:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 24 May 2021 08:07:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-25"}
